(198, 1, '2015-12-20 07:47:56', '2015-12-20 07:47:56', '[vc_row][vc_column][wr_about image="611" buttontext="Our projects" buttonurl="cases"]\r\n<h3><b>Who are we?</b></h3>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Crunch is a digital Agency, and has existed since 2010. It is both managed (administered) and founded by Adam Kischinovsky.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Our team has a wide knowledge regarding online visibility. Crunch is focusing on developing websites, design, advising on and developing marketing strategies.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><b>Our philosophy</b></h3>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">At Crunch the job isn’t done until our customers are 120% satisfied with the final result.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Many of our works come from references from other potential costumer. Therefore we put great honor in excellent service that leaves the customer fully satisfied.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">After we finish the job, we don’t forget our customer. We make sure that our service and the product we have developed , are future proof and, of course, we help the customer to continuously update their website, so that it is trendy and timeless in the same time.</span>[/wr_about][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2016-04-27 11:13:05', '2016-04-27 11:13:05', '', 0, 'http://webredox.net/demo/wp/dogma/demo1/?page_id=187', 0, 'page', '', 0),
