(459, 1, '2016-04-13 09:28:15', '2016-04-13 09:28:15', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">You’ve probably heard of these terms, but only have a basic or no idea what they stand for. It is quite important for everyone who is about to get a personal or business website to understand the main differences between these two types of websites in order to make the best choice. </span>\r\n\r\nIn this short article, you can find the main advantages and disadvantages of static and dynamic websites.\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">As a regular Internet user, you may have noticed the contrast between some websites in means of functionality and updated content. However, for someone who is a non-professional, it might be hard to understand why and how websites differ. It is important for you to be aware of the opportunities you have for developing your personal or company website.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<b>Static websites</b>\r\n\r\nThe majority of static websites look quite simple, without many interactions on the site itself. They are easy to develop but harder to update and they are usually used by small companies that want to provide basic information to their customers.\r\n\r\n<strong>Advantages:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">cheap development</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">cheap hosting services</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">quick development</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Disadvantages:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">hard for non-professionals to update</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">content could become stagnant </span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">less useful for the user</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Dynamic websites have the potential to give the users a better experience since it is easy for the owner to update and create content. Dynamic websites are becoming more and more common because of their usability both for owners and users.</span>\r\n\r\n<strong>Advantages:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">more functional than static websites</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">easier to update and create content</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">allow for collaboration between owner and user</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">greater chance of maintaining the user’s attention and interest </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Disadvantages:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">more expensive to develop</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">take more time to develop </span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">more expensive hosting services</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">take more time to update content</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDespite the fact that there are still many static sites, many people are discovering the benefits of having a dynamic website. A dynamic website could be a better choice for you since you can use it as a tool to design a professional, interesting experience for your visitors.', 'Static vs Dynamic websites', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '455-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-13 09:28:15', '2016-04-13 09:28:15', '', 455, 'http://wearecrunch.net/newsite/2016/04/13/455-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(460, 1, '2016-04-13 10:47:32', '2016-04-13 10:47:32', '<span style="font-weight: 400; color: #000000;">If you are one of the people who still wonder if they should spend time and money on online marketing, we advise you to continue reading. It is becoming more and more popular for any kind and size of businesses to show up online. But you don’t have the extra budget to spend this year on something that you are not sure is going to work for you? Well, if you need some reasons to convince you, here are ours: </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><strong>An easy and fast way to reach more people </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">If you are reading this, it means that you are one of the</span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a style="color: #000000;" href="http://www.statista.com/statistics/273018/number-of-internet-users-worldwide/"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 3,17 billion Internet users</span></a></span><span style="font-weight: 400;">. A huge number, isn’t it?  Of course, you won’t reach all of them but for sure you will expand your reach. Whether you are trying to reach youngsters or middle-aged, even our grandparents have access to the Web these days. </span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Being visible online in the world of constant browsing can be crucial for your business. With your own website or blog, you will be able to show the World your products/services in a modern way and expand your reach.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">Social media is also a huge part of our everyday life. It gives you the opportunity to connect to and communicate with your customers and present yourself as a professional in your area of work.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Cost effective </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">The budget is one of the most important parts of your business plan. When deciding whether or not to show up on the Internet, you might think that it could influence your budget in a negative way but consider this - the long term investment that you are making getting a company website will pay you back faster than you’ve imagined.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;">There are also quite a few things you can do to promote our business online for free. For example, getting a Facebook or LinkedIn company page or sharing thoughts and pictures on twitter and Instagram. You can read more about your social media marketing opportunities here: (link to the other blog post)</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Additional advertising and sales tool</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400; color: #000000;">In the virtual world, the size of your company does not really matter. With a good online marketing strategy, you can out rank in Google big international competitors. In fact, there are more small businesses that are still invisible online, so this might be a huge benefit for you to go ahead of the others and give your customers more. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Consider also using social media to display for free your products or services. As </span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><a style="color: #000000; text-decoration: underline;" href="http://www.hubspot.com/company/management/brian-halligan"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Brian Halligan</span></a></span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> said</span><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">:” To be successful and grow your business and revenues, you must match the way you market your products with the way your prospects learn about and shop for your products.”</span></i></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Bigger impact </strong></span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400; color: #000000;">All good managers know that if you are following the latest trends, you are highly competitive and people are more likely to ask for your products or services. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="color: #000000;">Expanding your reach and establishing a good reputation online, gives you the opportunity to build better customer relationships and consequently attract new and bigger clients.</span> </span>', 'The importance of being present on the Internet', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-being-present-on-the-internet-is-so-important-for-your-business', '', '', '2016-04-13 10:52:08', '2016-04-13 10:52:08', '', 0, 'http://wearecrunch.net/newsite/?p=460', 0, 'post', '', 0),
