(463, 1, '2016-04-13 10:16:21', '2016-04-13 10:16:21', '<span style="font-weight: 400;">You have come to the decision to get a website. And now you are trying to figure out whether you need to hire some professionals to do it or use the services provided by website builders. If you haven’t heard of them, we will describe them shortly for you - they are online tools that allow you to create a website without manual coding.  </span>\r\n\r\nAt first sight, it might sound super cool and cost effective but in fact, there are a few benefits of hiring a professional web designer to do the work for you.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Fresh and modern look - web designers know how to make your website look modern because their job is to keep up with the latest trends in web design. </span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Saving you time - no matter how easy to use one website builder is, it will take some time that you might not have. A good web designer will only need a few meetings and as a result, you will receive a professional  website quickly.</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Expressing your values - an experienced web designer will take the right path to present your identity in the best way so your website will communicate the message representing your business.</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Provide you with a unique website - good web designers are creative and they take every project individually. A professional will design something original based on your company’s values as well as the newest trends in web design. This means that in the end you are going to have a user-friendly website that stands out and attracts the attention of the right people. </span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Highlight your strengths - a competent designer knows how to expose your best products or services and focus on your finest asset. This will give you a credible and expert look.</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Make you trustworthy - with the right images and text a proper web designer can find the perfect way make the visitors of your website trust you as an expert in your field and it is worth doing business with you. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">After all, it is up to you to decide if you want to hire a professional web designer instead of building the website yourself. </span>\r\n\r\nConsidering the benefits we’ve listed above together with the fact that you will only pay one time and then a small amount of money for hosting services (while most website builders require monthly payment), it is a good idea to invest in a professional assistance for the optimal results.', 'Why do I need a web designer?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'why-do-i-need-a-web-designer', '', '', '2016-04-13 10:16:21', '2016-04-13 10:16:21', '', 0, 'http://wearecrunch.net/newsite/?p=463', 0, 'post', '', 0),
