c_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][wr_text_block title="Online Marketing" image="423"]\r\n<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Strategy:</span></h3>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Your marketing strategy is how, what, where, when and to whom you plan to deliver your brand messages. Where you advertise is a crucial part of your marketing. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">We will  help you promote your business on social media and give you appropriate advice on paid advertisement on the Internet.</span>\r\n<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">SEO:</span></h3>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">SEO is short for search engine optimization, and yes, a website should definitely be optimized for search engines. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">We will assist you to find the best search words for your industry and market, so you can overtake your competitors on the search engines.</span>[/wr_text_block][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][wr_text_block title="Design" imgposition="st1" image="425"]\r\n<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Here we come!</span></h3>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">You need a new logo or you think that your existing one is quite old? </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">We are going to create the logo you dream of and we won’t stop until you are 100% satisfied with the result. </span>Also, we can create posters, brochures, business cards and many more for you so you can promote your brand successfully.\r\n<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Branding:</span></h3>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Branding is pretty much the most important aspect of any kind of business - small or big , retail or B2B. An effective brand strategy can give you a step ahead in the increasingly competitive market world.</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Your logo is the cornerstone of your brand . Your website and promotional materials should be integrated with your logo in order to communicate your brand in the best possible way.</span>\r\n\r\n[/wr_text_block][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][wr_text_block title="Support" image="426"]\r\n<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">Save money with our support clip cards.</span></h3>\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Now you can get a discount on normal hourly rates by purchasing a clip card. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">The clip cards can be used for the maintenance of your website. </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Normally, the payment is done per hour but with a clip card it’s calculated per 15 minutes. </span>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Voucher system can be used for the following:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Updating the content of the page</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Minor adjustments to the design</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">General support for the administration system</span></li>\r\n	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Support if there are any errors</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/wr_text_block][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Service', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '177-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-27 10:37:26', '2016-04-27 10:37:26', '', 177, 'http://wearecrunch.net/newsite/2016/04/27/177-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
